Feedforward — “Answer Trying Phase”

ANN first tries to give an answer using the input data.

Real-Time Example: You Throw a Ball into Basket 🏀

You throw the ball toward the basket.

At this moment:

You are only trying
You don’t know whether it is correct or wrong yet

This is exactly Feedforward.

=====


Input → Network → Prediction(Output)

======

ANN Example

Suppose:

Input = Student studies 2 hours daily

ANN predicts:

"Student will PASS"

Here ANN only gives prediction.
No correction yet.



